The Independent National Electoral Commission (INEC) has announced fresh recruitment. The agency announced recruitment of Registration Area Officers, Administrative Officers and Executive Officers in all local government areas of the country. INEC urged interested candidates to log on to its portal www.inecnigeria.org /www.inecrecruitment.com to complete the prescribed application free of charge. INEC in a newspaper advertorial on Monday added: ”Applicants should not be above 35 years while the experienced applicants should not be above 45 “Applicants must possess Nation Certificate Examination or Nation Diploma (ND) with a minimum of two years post-qualification cognate experience ”Candidates should log on to www.inecnigeria.org /www.inecrecruitment.com to complete the prescribed application free of charge.”